                                Toyota is ramping up its electric vehicle efforts with a significant investment in battery technology, aiming to roll out 10 new EV models by 2025.
                            </p>
                            <a href="#" class="btn btn-default01">Read More</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="d-flex flex-column justify-content-between mx-4">
                    <div class="card" style="width: 20rem;">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">Ford F-150 Lightning Dominates Truck Market</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">
                                The electric Ford F-150 Lightning has become a bestseller, with its impressive towing capacity and extended range capturing attention nationwide.
                            </p>
                            <a href="#" class="btn btn-default01">Read More</a>
