                            <a href="#" class="btn btn-default01">Read More</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="d-flex flex-column justify-content-between mx-4">
                    <div class="card" style="width: 20rem;">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">Porsche Expands EV Lineup with Macan EV</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">
                                Porsche's upcoming Macan EV is set to offer sporty performance and luxury in an electric SUV format, aiming to compete with Tesla's Model Y.
                            </p>
                            <a href="#" class="btn btn-default01">Read More</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card" style="width: 20rem;">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">Honda CR-V Hybrid Gains Popularity</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">
                                The Honda CR-V Hybrid has seen a surge in sales thanks to its improved fuel efficiency, advanced safety features, and affordable price point.
                            </p>
                            <a href="#" class="btn btn-default01">Read More</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="d-flex flex-column justify-content-between mx-4">
                    <div class="card" style="width: 20rem;">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">Chevrolet Bolt EV Offers Unmatched Value</h5>
